Here i want to share how my personal cicd works. Thanks to Golang it costs me only 5$ digitalocean instance which runs - traefik, grafana, promethues, loki and my personal sites. Hope it will be helpful&hellip;
First of all list of used tools:
 Traefik - as reverse proxy with lets encrypt Github - as git repository Docker Hub - as docker images registry, and build tool Watchtower - refreshes running container with new version  You can find all of the code here
